longBusinessSummary: Safeture AB (publ) operates as a software as a service company. It offers cloud-based services that manage employee risk, safety, and crisis processes. The company was formerly known as GWS Production AB (publ) and changed its name to Safeture AB (publ) in June 2019. Safeture AB (publ) was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
